---
---

<section
  id="about"
  aria-labelledby="about-heading"
  class="py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-[var(--c-border)]"
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20 items-center">

    <!-- Left: visual card -->
    <div class="reveal order-2 md:order-1">
      <div
        class="relative rounded-2xl bg-[var(--c-surface)] border border-[var(--c-border)] p-8 glow-green-lg overflow-hidden"
        role="complementary"
        aria-label="Quick facts about Kyle"
      >
        <!-- Circuit-line background -->
        <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 grid-lines opacity-50"></div>

        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Icon -->
          <div
            class="w-14 h-14 rounded-xl bg-[#2D5016]/10 border border-[#2D5016]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <svg aria-hidden="true" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="w-7 h-7 text-[#2D5016]">
              <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <!-- Quick facts -->
          <dl class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-[var(--c-border)] pb-3">
              <dt class="text-[var(--c-text-mut)] text-sm">Day job</dt>
              <dd class="text-[var(--c-text-pri)] text-sm font-medium">Energy Efficiency Consulting</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-[var(--c-border)] pb-3">
              <dt class="text-[var(--c-text-mut)] text-sm">Location</dt>
              <dd class="text-[var(--c-text-pri)] text-sm font-medium">Portland, OR</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-[var(--c-border)] pb-3">
              <dt class="text-[var(--c-text-mut)] text-sm">Night shift</dt>
              <dd class="text-[var(--c-text-pri)] text-sm font-medium">SaaS, tools, agents, courses</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center pb-0">
              <dt class="text-[var(--c-text-mut)] text-sm">Stack</dt>
              <dd class="text-[var(--c-text-pri)] text-sm font-medium">Python · TypeScript · React · Claude</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: text -->
    <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
      <span class="reveal text-[#2D5016] text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium" aria-hidden="true">About</span>

      <h2
        id="about-heading"
        class="reveal mt-3 font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--c-text-pri)] leading-tight"
        data-delay="1"
      >
        Energy efficiency consultant by day, software builder by night.
      </h2>

      <p class="reveal mt-5 text-[var(--c-text-sec)] leading-relaxed" data-delay="2">
        I close 50+ Portland retrofits a year at Resilient Retrofits and ship automation tools — SnuggSpec (in pilot with field auditors), Scraping School (Python course in build-in-public mode), and an overnight Claude Code system that runs 14 jobs while I sleep.
      </p>

      <p class="reveal mt-4 text-[var(--c-text-sec)] leading-relaxed" data-delay="3">
        The day job is deeply technical and deeply human: sitting at kitchen tables helping families make expensive, lasting decisions about heat pumps, insulation, and electrification — then filing the rebate stack so they pay as little as possible.
      </p>

      <p class="reveal mt-4 text-[var(--c-text-sec)] leading-relaxed" data-delay="4">
        Nights I build. I use Claude and MCP-powered agents to automate the repetitive stuff — research, writing, QA, code — so my focused hours go toward the problems that actually require a human. If it can run overnight, I want it running overnight.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
